trucks.name: Slice-A-Pizza
trucks.about: Traditional 1980's American Pizzeria-style take on pizza, made to order. Not gourmet & not wood-fired. Choose from our infamous Cheese Bread, BBQ Chicken Pizza or Pizza Pocket. Ask about our Gluten-free/ Keto crust option that everyone's raving about!

trucks.name: Super Taqueria
trucks.about: We could be just another average taqueria, but we're not - we're the Super Taqueria! From tacos to tamales, fajitas, chimichangas, and more, you're sure to find a Super Taqueria something that will satisfy your tastebuds. Make your meal truly super with one of our desserts!

trucks.name: Tandoor Taco
trucks.description: Yummy Garlic Naan flatbread open-faced sandwiches
trucks.about: Tandoor Taco brings the best of two worlds with their famous clay-oven baked naan flatbreads filled with Indian Classics and other Globally-Inspired Creations. Try the Curry Chicken Tikka Masala, Cilantro Lime, or Garbanzo Veggie. Each naan’wich comes with lettuce, tomatoes, and shredded cheese. You can skip the bread and turn any naan’wich into a salad. You’re going to love it!

trucks.name: LULU'S CHURROS
trucks.description: Lulu's Churros, is the result of a special recipe, the best ingredients and the dedication of its owners and staff, served with quality and special care.

trucks.name: Snowie of Tooele County
trucks.about: We sell Snowie snow cones and provide full service catering and event rentals.

trucks.name: Leroy's Cowboy Sushi
trucks.about: Sushi without fish...say whaa? We offer a unique twist to the traditional way of sushi. Think of grilled steak or chicken, smoked pulled pork with fresh and crisp veggies rolled in a soy paper wrap and rice topped with our tasty sauces and you have Cowboy Sushi. We affectionately call it ALL TURF, NO SURF! This is a taste experience you need to try.

trucks.name: Flourish Street food and sweets
trucks.description: The Flourish Bakery Food Truck is a social enterprise of Flourish Ventures, a 501(c)3 nonprofit organization dedicated to helping people with a history of incarceration and in early recovery from substance use disorder learn the skills necessary for total life transformation. The Flourish Food Truck offers a menu of savory street food and sweets, updated seasonally, and sources ingredients (as often as possible) from local and organic farmers and vendors in Utah. Come on by, try our food, and see what it means to build better people through the opportunity to begin again!

trucks.name: Gerlach's
trucks.about: Hot Dogs, Texas Chili Cheese, Brazilian Style, Spicy German, even Cuban style. All of our menu is available as vegan, even the Texas chili cheese! All of our additional toppings are free, lots of choices and we pile them on!

trucks.name: The Komrades
trucks.about: The Komrades team creates “Food For The People”– craft-made street eats featuring world flavors and international influences, that are fresh, fast and affordable. We serve sandwiches and salads with seasonal ingredients and skillful preparation!

trucks.name: Garden O’Veaten
trucks.description: Plant-based, Non-GMO, Gluten Free, Organic healthy fresh food
trucks.about: We aim to inspire whole food, plant-based eating and sustainable living. We believe that what we eat, and how we eat it, is the vital piece in the puzzle of total health and wellness for our bodies and our planet. This is a reach and teach vehicle, delivering the taste of change to the world!Your taste buds and body will BOTH love you for eating our healthy and DELICIOUS food - handcrafted, organic, non-GMO, and gluten free! Warning: our dishes are addicting! Try our Mac and Casheeze, Buddha and Baby Buddha bowl, or Ecstasy Energy bites. Can't wait to see you at our window!

trucks.name: Made In Brazil
trucks.about: Making mouths water with tantalizing aromas & authentic Brazilian recipes is our specialty.  Our amazing menu features traditional offers such as Feijoada, Coxinhas, pastel, brigadeiro, acai & much more!  For an unforgettable taste of this beautiful country’s flavors, make sure your next meal is from Made in Brazil!

trucks.name: SPECIAL COURSES
trucks.about: We are a food truck and eatery offering the Taste of Freedom w/ our Speciality Burgers, Freedom Fries & Military Grade Refreshments bit.ly/armychef

trucks.name: Credible Edibles
trucks.about: Credible Edibles is a Food Trailer that serves Utah’s best edible cookie dough.We have all different kinds of flavors like Original, Birthday Bash, Peanut Butter Love and Chocolate Explosion! All cookie doughs are made using heat-treated flour and without eggs! :)

trucks.name: Stir's
trucks.description: Changing the Way You Eat Cereal
trucks.about: With 25 different cereals we all know and love, Stir’s is “Changing the Way You Eat Cereal” We’ve got a wide variety of toppings and milks to make sure your bowl of cereal is just how you like it! Bring the nostalgia factor to a whole new level by enjoying a bowl of cereal with Stir’s!

menu_items.name: Traditional PR Style Rice, Roast Pork, Boricua Style Chicken,  Sweet and Savory Plantains, Empanadillas, and more

trucks.name: Papito Moes Puerto Rican Grub
trucks.about: Papito Moe's is bringing Puerto Rican Flavor to Utah! We’ve come to Utah hungry to share traditional island favorites with you...Can you say Pernil, Mofongo, Tostones Empanadillas, and more?! Come Savor the Taste of the Island and put some WEPA in your step!

trucks.name: test truck sample
trucks.about: test

trucks.name: The Pizza Bus
trucks.about: Pizza is always a good answer! The Pizza Bus offers quality food, great service, and fair prices. This truck can cater anything from wedding parties to family reunions. Book them for your next office lunch or midnight softball tournament. You absolutely cannot go wrong with a Classic Pepperoni or Triple Cheese pizza - and you’ll love the specialty pizzas like Chicken Bacon BBQ or Spicy Luau.  Be sure to snap a picture in front of the Pizza Bus, and ask owner Dave for a tour when it’s slow :)

trucks.name: RJ BBQ and Catering
trucks.about: RJ BBQ serving up some mouth-watering BBQ with delicious homemade sides! Try our brisket, pork belly or ribs and you’re sure to fall in love! Our sides are the perfect touch to any meal; bacon mac and cheese, BBQ baked beans or loaded potato salad. Finish off the meal with our fresh peach, blueberry or triple berry cobbler!

trucks.name: The Daily Shave Ice
trucks.about: Local fresh shave ice!

trucks.name: On The Hook
trucks.description: Best Wild Alaskan Cod Fish and Chips in the Mountain West!
trucks.about: Starting with the highest quality cod from the cold clean waters of Alaska caught using hook and line, each fish is brought aboard individually and immediately prepared to perfectly preserve the fresh caught quality and tenderness. Coated with our original recipe beer batter and paired with our homemade signature dipping sauces completes a perfect dish!

trucks.name: Abiyaki Hibachi Grill
trucks.description: The first hibachi/teppanyaki food truck in Utah. We cook your fresh meals by order. We specialized in typical Japanese steakhouse. Simply Delicious!

trucks.name: The Salty Pineapple
trucks.about: We are a Hawaiian style BBQ food truck located in Salt Lake City, UT. Bringing the Big Island taste we all love to the mainland! Our sweet garlic chicken and mouth watering pork sliders are just a hint of what we bring to the table!

trucks.name: The Corn Dog Company
trucks.about: We are home to the "honey-dog" which adds honey to our hot, made from scratch daily, cornbread style batter for a taste that is second to none. Our menu is small, but our flavors are huge! Top one off with Ketchup or Mustard and you're all set!

trucks.name: Hey! Soda
trucks.about: We're a local soda and cookie shop! Come say hello! Specialty sodas, cookies, popcorn, and pretzels.

trucks.name: Haole T's Beach Grill
trucks.description: Haole T’s Foodtruck and Catering, bringing Fusion Cuisine out of our 30ft mobile kitchen. Blended flavors of Hawaiian/ Asian to Mexican/ American from Beer Battered to order Fish and Chips to our Beach inspired 1/3lb Angus Beef Burgers and Rice Bowls, we have a flavor for everyone.

trucks.name: Crumbs Donuts
trucks.about: We start with delicious buttermilk mini cake donuts and load them with a variety of scrumptious toppings! Choose from cinnamon/sugar, maple, glaze, chocolate and more!

trucks.name: Thirs-T Specialty Drinks and Edible Cookie Dough
trucks.description: Fountain Drinks and Edible Cookie Dough
trucks.about: You can order a refreshing fountain drink and customize it with our menu of 20+ syrup flavors. Thirs-T also has edible cookie dough thats ready to eat. Choose from our rotating menu of flavors.

trucks.name: Thai Chef To Go
trucks.about: Thai Chef To Go serves freshly made Thai food crafted from the best ingredients. We serve Pad Thai and many curry dishes just to name a few!

trucks.name: Rolling Bistro
trucks.about: A Smoke a' Billy company, Rolling Bistro serves up delicious sandwiches with a barbeque twist! Try our Bourbon Tri-Tip Sandwich, Guinness Beer Brat with Onions, or our Char Siu Pork Sandwich! We can't wait to roll up and share our sandwiches with you!

trucks.name: Art City Donuts
trucks.about: Utah's Original Donut Truck bringing you Hot, Fresh, Gourmet, Mini Donuts. These hot, fresh mini donuts come drizzled with Art City’s own original icings!  Just one sniff or glimpse of these little beauties will get your mouth watering. Try our Shortcake, Coconut Cream, Lemon Bar, Cinnabon & Chocolate Cream Pie. Just one will definitely not do!

trucks.name: El Nene Sammy
trucks.description: Mexican Food with a Argentine Twist
trucks.about: Mexican Food with an Argentine twist. Try our amazing tacos, quesadillas, tostadas, or burritos with fresh and flavorful ingredients. Top it off with our famous Argentine Chimichurri sauce!

trucks.name: Cool Treats
trucks.about: Try our delicious, creamy, and tasty ice cream treats.  With everything from cones, sundaes, shakes, and floats we can satisfy whatever your ice cream craving is!  Cool Treats is the place to get the coolest treats in town and cool off in the HOT sun.

trucks.name: Donut Kabobs
trucks.description: Mini Donuts on a Stick! Served out of a 60's retro trailer
trucks.about: We offer unique donut kabobs that make your donut eating experience less messy and even more tasty, we also have a wide variety of toppings and if you have not tried our specialty baskets they are a thing of beauty! Maple bacon, Nutella banana, caramel apple, and cookies n cream!

trucks.name: Heidi Cakes Utah
trucks.about: What started out as a Bake Sale to raise money for our Annual Anti Drug & Alcohol Rally; took on a life of it's own and became a business! We have delicious, made from scratch gourmet cupcakes! Choose from Double Vanilla, Lemon Pie, Chocolate Truffle or Salted Turtle just to name a few!

trucks.name: Dippin Dots
trucks.about: A unique futuristic ice cream in tiny dots that kids love! We also serve  root beer and orange floats as well as sundaes using the dots!  It's a fun  and refreshing treat for the whole family!

trucks.name: Wings on Wheels
trucks.about: A food truck/catering business with great customer service that is dedicated to serving fresh and delicious food. Our delicious wings are served with homemade sauces that will make your taste buds fall in love. Come and enjoy! We cater. Ask for the menu.

trucks.name: Clark's Malasadas
trucks.about: A malasada is a Portuguese donut, without a hole, that was made popular by Hawaii. You can find them everywhere in Hawaii, but they aren't as common here in Utah! The malasadas that we make will all be rolled in either sugar, or cinnamon and sugar. You can also have them filled with different flavors of custards and creams.

menu_items.name: Cinnamon-dusted Plantains with Cucumber Curry Mayo

trucks.name: KAFE MAMAI
trucks.about: From the Swahili coast of Lamu to the shores of Montego Bay, from Mofongo to Fufu, I prepare traditional and delicious African and Caribbean fusion cuisine

trucks.name: Hunt's Texas BBQ
trucks.about: Texas Flavor on the go! Try our sliced brisket tender smoked low and slow, our pork riblets of three flavors, or our juicy and bold chicken quarter. Order with a side of South Texas style pinto beans or seasoned kernel's bacon fried corn, then finish with our frito pie and you've got a true Texas meal!

trucks.name: 801coffee roasters
trucks.about: 801 is a local coffee roasting company in Salt Lake City, Utah sharing the wonders of our coffee by means of a mobile vending truck

trucks.name: Momo's Gourmet Cheesecake Co
trucks.description: Custom Cheesecakes for events and personal orders
trucks.about: The best most delicious cheesecakes you have ever had.  We can create any cheesecake you can dream of.   For events we can provide our famous mini size super cute cheesecakes, our 4” Personals, or our bigger sized 8”, 9” and 10”.   For weddings we can also make two or three tier cheesecakes.  All of our sauces are made in house with the freshest ingredients.  We have over 30 flavors and offer a variety of crust options.

trucks.name: Black’s Sliders
trucks.description: SLIDERS, beef, fried chicken , pulled pork and vegetarian options, along with 3 kinds of fries.
trucks.about: Our food is hormone and antibiotic free and purchased from Wasatch meats , a local  vendor who holds the same vision of health through product excellence. We serve a variety of sliders and fries that everyone will love! Enjoy a choice of beef, chicken, pork or vegetarian sliders with toppings like cheddar cheese, caramelized onions & an array of fresh vegetables!  Don’t forget a side of our amazing, uniquely flavored fries!

menu_items.name: Ooie Gooie • Pepperoni • MeatHead • Island • Loaded • SLB • Garlic Knots • Sweet Cones and much more

trucks.name: Pizza Cone Zone
trucks.about: Golden Pizza Dough in the shape of a cone, stuffed with  the highest quality meats and cheeses - baked on site to perfection. So unique, so different, so delicious • You really can put Pizza in a Cone!!

trucks.name: Bruges
trucks.description: Sharing the joy of Belgium's best loved foods
trucks.about: Since 2004, Bruges shares the best loved foods from Belgium with Utah. Their food is not only fun, but it is authentic, artisan made with natural ingredients and prepared fresh for you. Try their unique sweet caramelized Liège waffle, award winning fries (frites) or famous Machine Gun Sandwich. Experience true Belgian indulgence without the jetlag.

trucks.name: Freshies Lobster Co
trucks.description: Maine lobster rolls and  New England foods.
trucks.about: It started with two  New Englanders selling lobster rolls out of a 10x10 tent 10 years ago in Park City, they now have a restaurant and food truck in the Park City and Salt Lake area.  They are know for their very authentic and delicious Lobster Roll.  They do this by shipping in the lobster fresh from the shores of Maine and the bread is shipped from Maine as well.  Try our perfected, traditional, New England style fresh lobster roll (voted “World’s Best Lobster Roll” at the “Down East Lobster Roll Festival” competition in Portland, Maine!), lobster sliders, salads and more.

menu_items.name: French Toast or Bread Pudding- topped with fresh whipped cream, mixed berries and one of our signature sauces.
Soups-  White Chili, Coconut Curry, Creamy Tomato.
Grilled Cheese - Mozzerrella, Pepperjack, Cheddar, Swiss.
Loaded Grilled Cheese- Turkey Pesto Mozzerella, Roast Beef and Swiss, Tuna Melt, Ham and Cheddar, Turkey Pepperjack.
Specialty Drinks - Hot Chocolate, Frozen Hot Chocolate, Frozen Lemonade

trucks.name: The Lost Bread
trucks.description: Comfort Food that rivals grannies cookin'
trucks.about: We started as a French Toast, and Bread Pudding truck, but as we grew and shared our creations we couldnt keep it to just a few items. Now we carry mouth watering soups, from coconut curry, to white chili, every bite is packed with flavor. To compliment our soups we also have Perfectly Toasted Grilled Cheese sandwiches as well as loaded grilled cheese sandwiches. Signature sauces compliment our sweet items and they are always topped with fresh berries and house whipped cream.

trucks.name: Leila's Luau
trucks.about: If you love Polynesian food, don't pass us up! We serve delicious polynesian plates with Kalua Pork, Teriyaki Chicken, Rice and Hawaiian Mac Salad. Still not satisfied? For dessert we have Pineapple Ice Cream Boats and Malasadas!

trucks.name: Yuchi Crispy Crepes
trucks.about: Two foodies just want to share their crepes with everyone! At Yuchi Crepes we create crepes with savory toppings and flavorful fillings. Each flavor is designed by our creative chef and made from scratch.

trucks.name: S'Mothered @Collier's Corner
trucks.description: Made from scratch S’Mothered chili verde and sweet pork nachos, burritos,, and rice bowls.  Yummy!!
trucks.about: I am the original S’Mother now promoted to Grand S’’Motherer, which just happens to be my style of cooking.  Made from scratch S’Mothered goodness!!!!

trucks.name: Huckleberry Grill LLC
trucks.about: Huckleberry Grill is the food truck to call for fresh ingredients, delicious food, and a top-notch dining experience. Vegan, vegetarian, and gluten free menus available!

menu_items.name: Tacos carne asada, taco fish, barbecue beef
Tacos asada, fish, shrimp and chicken

trucks.name: Rio Sonora
trucks.about: fresh ingredients= amazing food.we cook the best tacos, nachos, burttios, quesadillas and our killer hot dog sonora style.

trucks.name: Waffle Stop & Authentic Salvadorean Cafe
trucks.about: We are a “breakfast all day” truck - we have waffles whenever you want them, morning ‘till night! Among our breakfast foods, we also serve authentic Salvadorian food, so whether you want an apple pie cinnamon waffle for dinner or pupusas for lunch, you’re sure to find something to love!

trucks.name: Porteña Gourmet Empanadas
trucks.about: Flavors of home at your fingertips! Gourmet, fresh baked Argentinian empanadas.  We use a wide variety of flavors & textures, our empanadas are made with fresh seasonal ingredients that can satisfy your savory and sweet cravings.Porteña is proud to offer empanadas, a pastry pocket stuffed with a filling of your choice, that are meant to be shared around the table with your loved ones. We don't just feed people - we nourish them.

trucks.name: Monchi’s mexican grill
trucks.about: The best variety of authentic Mexican flavors in Utah! We serve up Tacos, Fajitas, Burritos, Torta, Papas Asadas and Hamburgers! Try one of our specialties, La Pirata or La Gringa! Real food, real Mexican taste!

trucks.name: Tandooria
trucks.about: University of Utah food truckIndian and Thai cuisine rice bowls

trucks.name: Mamas mobile toasted cheeser
trucks.about: We serve a variety of gourmet toasted cheese sandwiches and fresh cut fries.  We use premium and fresh ingredients which stand out from the crowd.  If you love cheese, you will love us! Premium toasted cheese sandwich and fresh cut fries.

trucks.name: Sconey Island
trucks.description: The best gourmet scones you've ever had!
trucks.about: Delicious hot fried bread with gourmet toppings served with gourmet flavored iced drinks in the summer and hot in the winter. Try our Raspberry Cheesecake scone with our refreshing flavored iced milk in the Summer or in the Winter a hot Cookie Butter Fudge scone with a gourmet flavored hot chocolate.

trucks.name: Massimo's Pizza
trucks.about: Eatalian on the street! A Tuscan family with the passion for traditional cooking and love for genuine fresh foods. We have always loved making pizza and focaccia from scratch with our grandmother’s recipe.  Prepared fresh every day and baked in a wood burning oven.

trucks.name: Good Grindz
trucks.about: Restaurant quality Hawaiian food from a food truck! Kalua pig, Teriyaki Chicken, Macaroni Salad, Chicken Katsu, Katsu Curry & more.

trucks.name: Forge Pizzeria
trucks.about: Forge is a Neapolitan pizzeria specializing in hand-crafted pizzas fired in their 800 degree wood oven! We use only the freshest ingredients making for warm, cheesy goodness all the way around! We also have a delicious gluten free menu as well.

menu_items.name: Po-Boy Sandwiches, Red Velvet Waffle & Chicken
Seafood Gumbo, Crawfish Etouffee, Red Beans & Rice

trucks.name: Taste of Louisiana
trucks.description: Iconic Fresh Louisiana Entrees, Side Dishes & Desserts "Food Like No Other"
trucks.about: Louisiana Native, Army Retiree, Jerrell Carter finds niche enhancing events by serving a “Taste of Louisiana”.

trucks.name: Cups And Cakes
trucks.about: Delicious baked goods including cupcakes, sugar cookies, cake truffles, brownie bars, and cotton candy.  Our business was started by our kids as a way to help children in foster care. We love what we do!

trucks.name: Dough Gods
trucks.about: Join us on a mythical confectionary journey worthy of Odysseus himself.  As a family owned purveyor of fine edible cookie-dough, we are on a quest to deliver a unique and educational dessert experience to the community we grew up in.  Whether you crave the cinnamon spice of Hades’ underworld, the cooling mint breeze of Poseidon’s sea, or the lemony zing of Zeus’ thunderbolts, we have a flavor to temp the palette of everyone’s inner child.

trucks.name: Melty Way Mobile
trucks.description: Gourmet Grilled Cheese on the go!
trucks.about: Utah’s destination for amazing, gourmet melts and more.  We offer comfort food taken to new heights.  It’s all melty, cheesy, and delicious.  It’s the perfect way, the Melty Way, to treat yourself.

trucks.name: Udder Rivals
trucks.about:
Udder Rivals ice cream carries 12 delicious flavors of scooped ice cream from BYU and USU creameries available in cups or on cones! The rivalry comes from the national collegiate ice cream competition each June. BYU and USU rank in the top 13 every year! Take the Udder Challenge and decide which creamery is your favorite!

With the ice cream of your dreams, Udder Rivals food truck is serving Utah scooped ice cream, sundaes, floats and cookies from both BYU and USU creameries!Try the Udder Challenge, a scoop of vanilla from each school, and vote for your favorite!

menu_items.name: Meat empanadas, cheese empanadas, vegan empanadas, completos (Chilean style hotdogs) steak sandwiches, alefajores, berlinés

trucks.name: Noemi’s Catering
trucks.about: Noemi's catering is an company that started from catering and now it has grown in to the food truck world. Noemi the owner/chef brings her Chilean food style to Utah. Noemi's experience comes from growing up in the countryside of Chile, learning how to cook and bake. When Noemi got older she opened up a bakery and ran it with her family. Later, Noemi moved to the USA. She was the head cook for the Chilean Community for many years. Now she is growing into the food truck world and wants to share with you the flavors of Chile.

trucks.name: DaKine Grindz
trucks.about: Born in the Philippines and raised in Maui, Hawaii, our creator put the two best foods together and brought it to Utah as Dakine Grindz - Hawaiian fare that includes a taste of the Philippines! Try our delicious kabobs or kalua pork; or our Filipino favorites like lumpia, pancit or pork adobo!

trucks.name: Hungry Hawaiian
trucks.about: The Hungry Hawaiian is a rebirth of my father's restaurant that was originally opened in 1978. We launched our restaurant in June 2017 and the food truck February 2018. Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

trucks.name: Ay Chato
trucks.description: Asado Argentinian Grill was founded in May 2017 simply because we could find much in the way of authentic food in Utah County.  Most things were Chain and we love to eat right.  We realized that Utah was missing out on real South American food particularly Argentinian Cuisine.  Great cuts of beef, fresh pastas, amazing desserts and much more.  In order to maintain a freezer and microwave free environment the hustle is real.  We make it fresh throughout the day.  It’s the only concept that works for us as that’s how we feed our children and that’s how we will feed you.  Check out our gourmet burgers, sandwiches, Asado fries and much more.  We decided to name our food trailer Asadito as it’s a Jr. Asado.  We hope you give us a shot and enjoy our traditional homemade fresh food.

trucks.name: Mother of All
trucks.about: With unique spices and beautiful presentation, Mother of All reminiscent of Sudan. Specialties include gima (a crispy potato dish of peas, beef, and Sudanese spices), sambusa (a triangular pastry filled with vegetables and spices), falafel (a deep-fried doughnut made of chickpea flour), and basbusa (a sweet, syrupy semolina cake). A typical menu consists of sambusa, falafel, rice, chicken and vegetables.

trucks.name: Sobe eats
trucks.about: Sobe eats culinary concepts is a sustainable, environmentally friendly and plant forward company with strong family and community values. Found by 3 brothers and accomplished professional local chefs with a strong passion. Hungry to share our culture and experience thru our 25+ culinary journey.

trucks.name: Bomb Dilla
trucks.about: Bombdilla is a LA flair food truck. We specialize on loaded quesadilla and loaded tater tots! We promise you Utah it's going to be the BOMB!

trucks.name: Halabs Jasmine Kitchen
trucks.description: Fresh, authentic Syrian food including vegan and gluten free options. Our most popular items include falafel, chicken shawarma wraps, and kabsah. We have an extended menu available for catering.
trucks.about: Halab's Jasmine Kitchen is a family run business bringing the tastes of our home country, Syria, to Salt Lake City. We use fresh ingredients to prepare delicious, affordable Syrian food.

trucks.name: El Sarten Italian Pasta
trucks.about: We offer a variety of Italian Pasta, homemade sauces and many toppings. We specialize in combining your likes into your pasta. You choose your pasta, sauce, and toppings. Then our International chef will create an amazing combination just for you. Your perfect pasta!

trucks.name: Curry Time
trucks.about: We are an Indian food truck brought to you by India House restaurant located in Sandy, UT. We have been serving our delicious Indian cuisine to customers since 2001! Curry Time serves gourmet Indian cuisine -- curries, flat breads, and much more!  Our curries are made from the freshest ingredients, and our flatbreads are made in our imported Tandoor clay oven. Now we are bringing that mouth watering curry to the streets!

trucks.name: Falafel Tree
trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

trucks.name: El Sarten Mexicano
trucks.about:
At El Sarten Food Truck, we take great pride in carefully preparing each meal by hand and made with love using authentic family recipes passed down from one generation to the next. It doesn't matter who you are, or where you're from, when you come to our restaurant, we treat you like family. 

Our menu features traditional dishes and southern cuisine along with a few of our own creations and twists on the classics. If you're looking to experience authentic local food, served in a casual and friendly atmosphere, come visit our Food Truck today.

trucks.name: Rickle's
trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

trucks.name: Blake's Gourmet
trucks.about: We offer 3 Unique Sliders (Mini Sandwiches) Each Week and Flavored French Fries. Our menu changes weekly so you'll want to keep coming back to see what we come up with next!

trucks.name: Lucky Slice Pizza
trucks.about: Award-winning New York style pizza! Try a classic like the New-Yorker & Pepperoni or our other popular picks like the Dub All-Star & Fire Island.  Prepared with handmade dough, from-scratch sauces, and freshly prepared toppings & ingredients to ensure unmatched quality & flavor. Each slice is 1/6 of a 20" pizza, which makes each slice nearly 53 square inches!

trucks.name: Banh Mi Time
trucks.about: We are a mobile food truck that serves Vietnamese style sandwiches, burritos and rice bowls. Stop here for the best Vietnamese dishes around! We use only the freshest ingredients for the most flavorful Vietnamese/American dishes. Enjoy a wonderful pulled pork or glazed chicken sandwich or Banh Mi burrito with a side of ribbon fries, or try our new rice bowl!

trucks.name: Marmalade Coffee Co 2.0
trucks.description: The Big Orange Truck with The Bearded Barista!

trucks.name: Smoke a Billy BBQ
trucks.about: Inspired by Rock a Billy and the best smoked and cooked meats around.  Our passion for authentic homestyle and original BBQ keeps us striving for the very best.  All of our entrees are made fresh to order - freshness & satisfaction guaranteed!

trucks.name: Cluck Truck
trucks.description: Serving Salt Lake and surrounding counties with the best Gourmet fried chicken wraps!
trucks.about: Do you love fried chicken? So do we! We serve fresh, delicious fried chicken wraps in a variety of tasty styles. Try the Original, a mango chipotle slaw with a honey chili drizzle or Greek, Hawaiian, Chinese or BBQ flavors!  Add a side of garlic parmesan fries for a real feast!All things Chicken! Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

trucks.name: The Llama Truck
trucks.about: Your new Peruvian food truck! We serve dishes seasoned just right, such as the Lomo Saltado, Parrillada, Salchipaps, and Quinoa Salad tossed in roasted red pepper dressing! All items come with our hand cut fries turned to gold by hot oil and our house made dipping sauce.

trucks.name: Facil Taqueria
trucks.about: Fácil is a farm to table food truck. We source responsibly, ethically and locally. Everything on the truck is handmade with  ingredients rigorously selected at the peak of freshness. Handmade tortillas all day everyday! #farmtotaco

trucks.name: Fatty Tuna Food
trucks.about: Fatty Tuna food truck thrives on presenting our customers with tasteful authentic sushi and ramen through texture, spices, local produce and fresh fish. Come try our delicious ramen options of Tonkotsu Ramen, Shoyu Ramen, or Miso Ramen. Each have their own unique flavor for you to enjoy. We also serve the ever-popular sushi rolls such as the California roll, Vegas roll, and others!

trucks.name: Fiore Pizza
trucks.about: We are a mobile pizzeria creating handmade Italian style pizzas using fresh local ingredients. Pizzas are prepared and baked on-site in our Neapolitan wood-fired brick oven.

trucks.name: Thieps Eats
trucks.about: Thieps Eats is an Asian street food truck! We serve up a variety of different items ranging from seaweed salad, takoyaki, pot stickers, teriyaki, curry and more!

trucks.name: Umani  Pizza Truck
trucks.description: Umani, the unknown element - the family element. Come taste our world class wood-fired pizza! Try our great specials, like the Criolla or Hawaii 2.0. Can't decide on just one? Get a half and half pizza!  Come. Partake. Umani.

menu_items.name: Flavors: Tigers Blood Blue Raspberry Mango Lime Orange Cotton Candy.    Ice Cream.   Sweetened condensed milk.     Whip cream.

trucks.name: Icy Mountain Shaved Ice
trucks.description: Boujee shaved ice the best summer treat. Vegan & Gluten free options.

trucks.name: The Red Food Truck
trucks.about: Delicious Peruvian-style sandwiches filled with savory meats & fresh veggies. Try our popular Lomo Saltado Sandwich. We start with a soft ciabatta roll loaded with grilled steak, peppers, onions and a special sauce that sets it apart from any sandwich you have ever had!

menu_items.name: Jerk Chicken with Rice & Peas, Coleslaw and Plantains
Beef Oxtail with Rice & Peas, Coleslaw and Plantains
Jerk Pork with Rice & Peas, Coleslaw and Plantains

trucks.name: Jamaica's Kitchen
trucks.description: Jamaica's Kitchen is bringing the flavors and vibe of authentic Jamaican food to Utah. We offer everything from spicy and sweet Jamaican Jerk chicken to coco bread and ting and even tender curry goat with rice and beans.

trucks.name: The Green Falafel & kabab
trucks.about: Serving you traditional Mediterranean cuisine! Try our delicious falafel sandwich, hummus topped with cilantro, chickpeas, and paprika, fresh tabouli, savory chicken sandwich, or crisp Mediterranean salad! With flavorful and fresh ingredients, you're sure to love our food!

trucks.name: Iceberg Shake Truck
trucks.about: You’re in luck, because we are taking the famous Iceberg Thick Shakes on the road! Come and get your shake on with all of your favorite shakes!

trucks.name: Annie's Crepes & Cakes
trucks.description: Looking for a treat? We serve crepes sure to satisfy!
trucks.about: Our crepes come in a variety of flavors in both sweet and savory categories. Wanting something different? Try one of our unique bubble waffles!

trucks.name: Shrimp Shak
trucks.about: Enjoy our freshly beer battered shrimp with our homemade cocktail sauce and amazing waffle fries.

trucks.name: Liv Pure Acai
trucks.description: We serve Acai bowls , gourmet toast and smoothies

trucks.name: Happy Camper Deli
trucks.about: Repurposed trailer turned specialty sandwich shop!

trucks.name: Marquesas Corndogs
trucks.about: Named after the television show Survivor Marquesas, these are a not your mama's frozen corndogs! We serve hand-dipped golden delicious corndogs, double-hand  battered dill pickle spears, tillamook cheese sticks and sweet fried candy bars.

trucks.name: La Catrina Chilequiles Flavors of Mexico
trucks.about:
Chilaquiles (CHēləˈkēlās)
A traditional Mexican dish served “Street Style".   A variety of mild to hot salsas over corn tortilla chips then topped with your choice of steak, chicken or pork (Pastor, Asada o Pollo) and a  variety of other authentic toppings. ¡Delicioso!

trucks.name: Silver Moon Taqueria
trucks.description: Come try our amazing fish tacos!
trucks.about: Utah's first fish taco food truck! With our 35 years of restaurant experience, Silver Moon Taqueria was built on a foundation of a love of cooking and eating delicious food, and sharing it with people you care about. We choose locally sourced, simple ingredients whenever possible and combine those with authentic Mexican flavors.Silver Moon provides fresh, quality Mexican food made from daily from scratch.Be sure to try our variety of salsa options ranging in heat with any of our tacos, burritos or other delicious food options.

trucks.name: J.Dawgs
trucks.description: DAWGS, SAUCE, CHIPS, DRINKS, GOOD TIMES!
trucks.about: Nearly 20 years ago I pawned my Fender Telecaster to rebuild a small red shack in a small town with a few simple ideas: that food should be simple, that tin foil is better than plates and that napkins are always optional. That shack became my favorite place on earth, where a hot grill, all-natural dawgs, and homemade buns served over a good conversation are always an man's best friend. Now we are bringing the shack to you.  Enjoy!-J

trucks.name: Corndog Commander
trucks.about: Specialty hand-dipped corndogs!  You can't top our all beef dog breaded in a deliciously thick, sweet and crispy cornmeal layer. Be sure to add a side of waffle fries - they’re seasoned to  crispy perfection!

trucks.name: Traditions Mobile Cafe
trucks.about: We aren't fast food, we're good food! We make gourmet sandwiches, burgers and hand cut fries. We source all our food locally and love bringing good food and happiness to everyone we serve!

trucks.name: Waffle Love
trucks.about: A delicious gourmet waffle truck making liege waffles that have a caramelized & crispy exterior with a moist & dense interior, topped off with savory or sweet toppings that will make you want more!

trucks.name: Smokin Star BBQ
trucks.description: Welcome to the meat mecca of Smokin Star BBQ
trucks.about: Welcome to the meat mecca of Smokin Star BBQ, which has perfected the art of slow cooked meats using the most flavorful, aromatic, perfectly seasoned cherry & pecan hardwood and self taught recipes. Our heaping platters or meat by the pound includes several daily meat choices as well as holiday specials. Our goal is to Serve bbq that gives one a foodgasmic experience!

menu_items.name: Philly Cheesesteak Sandwich, Beef on Weck, Portobello Pesto Veggie Sandwich, Fresh Cut Fries and Pies. Daily Specials!

trucks.name: Shylo's Mobile Cafe
trucks.about: Shylo’s Mobile Café is an amazing food truck that serves fresh and hearty artisan sandwiches, soups, fries and pies.  Shylo’s Mobile Café has the food truck industry by storm! We create a synergy of creative, quick, addicting dishes from our executive chef!

trucks.name: Renee's Cheesecake
trucks.description: We serve a variety of cheesecakes and desserts. Including our famous cheesecake in a jar, frog eye salad in a jar, and fudge in a jar.

trucks.name: Utah Killer Dogs llc
trucks.about: Our open flamed grilled Hot Dogs are 100% beef.  Our Killer sauce is sweet and spicy, & is the perfect complement to this spectacular Dog! Add a bag of crisp chips & an ice cold drink and you have the perfect meal.

trucks.name: Kona Ice
trucks.description: The Original🍧Shave Ice Truck of Utah 🚚
trucks.about: | Kona Ice is premium tropical shaved ice made with quality ingredients and stevia. We offer delicious crafted flavors with ice-cream and cream.🍧If you are looking for the perfect summer treat Kona ice caters all types of events - corporate, festival, schools, sports and much more! Kona Ice operates a one of a kind mobile truck 🚚 a Kiosk 🚙, sure to make a lasting impression and an indoor unit.

trucks.name: Smokin Roadside Grill
trucks.about: This truck is the realization of a dream and three years of hard work perfecting our rub to create a flavor you’ll simply fall in love with! Try for yourself any of our smoked to perfection meats and a delicious side!

trucks.name: Fry Me to the Moon, SLC
trucks.about: You want it, we fry it! Enjoy delicious Navajo tacos or fries smothered in chili or sweet pork and loaded with toppings of your choice. Complement that with a side of onion rings, mozzarella sticks or a melt in your mouth scone with honey butter or loaded as a dessert. Can't go wrong if it's fried!!

trucks.name: District Thai Fusion
trucks.about: "Thai so nice, you'll want to come back twice!" We serve up all the exotic flavors of authentic Thai food in traditional dishes to treat your tastebuds to a world of flavor. Start with an egg roll or a pork dumpling, then try one of our delectable curries or a pad thai entree! We have orange chicken and Teriyaki chicken, too!

menu_items.name: Combo #1 - Stuffed potato with ground meat, served your choice of one empanada, cilantro rice and salad.
Combo #2 - Half an avocado stuffed with your choice of shredded chicken salad or quinoa shrimp salad. Served with your choice of an empanada, cilantro rice and salad.
Combo #4 - Peruvian style marinated stir fry beef sirloin served on a bed of French fries and rice.

trucks.name: Amkha Misky Peruvian Specialties
trucks.description: Hello all ! Come visit us and try some delicious Peruvian food!
trucks.about: We are a small family that love our culture and our cuisine. We love sharing our gastronomy with the beautiful state of Utah because we know how amazing it is. We hope you grow to love Peruvian food as much as we do and hope that it opens doors to exploring the beautiful culture that Peru holds.Come try our delicious empanadas which come in meat and vegetarian options or any of our other Peruvian specialties!

trucks.name: Jurassic Street Tacos
trucks.about: Jurassic Tacos started by us selling tacos from the back of a truck, to now having two trailers to feed the Jurassic size hunger of Salt Lake City and Utah. Our goal at Jurassic Street Tacos is to make sure the tacos you eat from us are the most delicious, biggest, and most talked about in the state of Utah.

trucks.name: With love ravioli
trucks.description: are italian-themed truck provides top quality food, with fast and friendly service,.
trucks.about: With Love Ravioli is an Italian/Italian themed food truck. . Ravioli is our staple, but we do offer much more than that. We also provide meatball and or sausage sandwiches, caprese sandwiches for our vegetarian guests, daily pasta specials, specialty salads and more. Chef Rachel has over 20 yrs of professional culinary experience. Chef Rachels passion for food started at a very young age. Rachel started her professional training in New York at the age of 16 . Since has had the amazing opportunity to train with Chefs from all over the world .  We do cater more than just Ravioli and Italian/italian themed cuisine . Our guests pick the theme and setting either With love ravioli food truck or we bring our supplies to the kitchen of your choice. We always aim to exceed our guests expectations.

trucks.name: Strippin Dippin Chicken
trucks.description: Home-made special dipping sauces that are perfect for dunking our lightly breaded chicken strips in. Chicken strips come in a 2-, 3- or 4-piece meal served with crispy golden fries. Sauces also work great as a salad dressing for our gluten free options. All served to order.

trucks.name: Yoshi's Enso Grill
trucks.about: Yoshi's Enso Grill is the food truck version of the popular Yoshi's Japanese Grill in Salt Lake City.  😀  We have sweet and spicy flavors in our rice bowls, sushi, egg rolls and more! We're sure we have something you will enjoy!

trucks.name: CupBop
trucks.about: 'CUPBOP' is a new trend in Korean style take-out food. Korean BBQ in a cup! CupBop uses an amazing blend of spices & sauces to top your choice of rice, noodles, vegetables, pork, chicken or beef! Choose hot & spicy or sweet & tangy! Indulge in this Korean BBQ layered with pure goodness! Korean style veggie noodles with rice and a seasonal menu are also available.

menu_items.name: Apollo burger, Bacon cheeseburger, Cheeseburger, Gyros, Utah burgers,fries and drinks

trucks.name: Apollo Truck
trucks.about: We char-broil our burgers to order, serve only the most delicious french fries we could find, compose our salads on the spot, and offer our own signature sandwiches, desserts, sauces and salad dressings. Add fresh lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and our homemade Apollo sauce to your burger with a lightly toasted, cornmeal bun.

trucks.name: South of the Border Tacos
trucks.about: Delicious Mexican food! Try our burritos, tacos, tortas, quesadillas, or especially our supreme nachos! Everything is fresh made from scratch!

trucks.name: San Diablo Artisan Churros
trucks.about: Our artisan churros are made from scratch, deep-fried fresh on-demand to golden perfection, coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon and then filled with your choice of sweet decadence like dulce de leche, nutella, sweet cream or seasonal (piña colada, strawberry lemonade, coconut cream, pumpkin cheesecake, caramel apple etc) and customized filling flavors and colors (to match whatever theme you have).

trucks.name: Churrology
trucks.description: Fresh. Fun. Fast. Hot churros made to order!
trucks.about: Our churros are made from scratch! Top with chocolate, strawberry, caramel, or sweet icing - we know everybody has their favorite! You can also try our Churro Tots - each order comes with a choice of 2 or 4 dipping flavors. Also available for private events, parties and corporate bookings.

trucks.name: Comfort Bowl
trucks.about: Just what it says . . . comfort food in a bowl! You’ll love their Japanese-style fried chicken and veggies covered with a sweet & spicy sauce. All of their bowls come included with lemongrass steamed rice and a Thai salad. Toss a few spring rolls on the side - you are sure to walk away pleased!Be sure to try their chicken katsu, which is their best seller. You won't be disappointed!

trucks.name: Family Squeezed Lemonade
trucks.about: Our fresh ingredients are chopped, sliced & smashed right before your eyes.  Nothing from mix or concentrate.  Throw in a little sugar, some ice & water, and your beverage is ready for you. It’s easy to like lemonade, it’s easier to LOVE award-winning Family Squeezed Lemonade!

trucks.name: The Smoked Taco
trucks.description: We combine BBQ Flavors with Tacos. Our Tacos are primarily made with Smoked Meats. We also offer Loaded Masa Fries which are corn flour based fries topped with delicious topping and Smoked Meat. Lastly, we offer Churro Fries with a rotation of seasonal flavors such as Salted Caramel, Strawberries and Cream, Peaches and Cream, Dolce de Leche and more.

trucks.name: The Ramen
trucks.about: Our menu features 5 main ramen dishes built upon a yummy broth soup. Spice it up or add some soy sauce for a terrific flavor. Top it off with sprouts, green onions, boiled egg, corn & a slice of pork roast!

menu_items.name: Firire Alloco: Grilled chicken, fries, fried plantains, onion sauce
Mafé:Peanut butter stew, rice, couscous, meat
Jolof Rice: Seasoned fried rice, choice of meat
Yassa: Lemony onion sauce over rice or couscous, choice of meat

trucks.name: Balabe Senegalese Cuisine
trucks.description: offering Authentic Senegalese Cuisine with vegan and gluten free options
trucks.about: Beautiful Food Truck offering authentic Senegalese Cuisine at various events, festivals and office Lunches. Concession and Catering in Salt Lake Valley.  Started in 2018 with by a Senegalese Cuisine cook from New York City named Pape Sall.

trucks.name: Kia Ora Kiwi
trucks.about: Kia Ora Kiwi is one of the few authentic places that you can eat New Zealand food in Utah!

trucks.name: Gnarly Island Grill
trucks.about: For a refreshing cool treat, Gnarly’s Island Grill’s pineapple dole whips (pineapple flavored soft serve) will hit the spot while helping you beat the heat.

trucks.name: Buzzed Coffee
trucks.description: Coffee and Pastry Truck [NO DRIVER ATTACHED]
trucks.about: Enjoy some heaven in a cup! We serve Gourmet Coffee, Espresso, Macchiato, Cappuccino, Latte, Mocha, Hot Chocolate and Tea! Don’t forget a scrumptious pastry to top it off!

attending_trucks.name: Thieps Eats
attending_trucks.about: Thieps Eats is an Asian street food truck! We serve up a variety of different items ranging from seaweed salad, takoyaki, pot stickers, teriyaki, curry and more!

attending_trucks.name: The Lost Bread
attending_trucks.about: We started as a French Toast, and Bread Pudding truck, but as we grew and shared our creations we couldnt keep it to just a few items. Now we carry mouth watering soups, from coconut curry, to white chili, every bite is packed with flavor. To compliment our soups we also have Perfectly Toasted Grilled Cheese sandwiches as well as loaded grilled cheese sandwiches. Signature sauces compliment our sweet items and they are always topped with fresh berries and house whipped cream.

events.name: The Lost Bread
events.description: Comfort Food that rivals grannies cookin'

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

events.original_name: Venture Out Food Truck Round Up

attending_trucks.name: District Thai Fusion
attending_trucks.about: "Thai so nice, you'll want to come back twice!" We serve up all the exotic flavors of authentic Thai food in traditional dishes to treat your tastebuds to a world of flavor. Start with an egg roll or a pork dumpling, then try one of our delectable curries or a pad thai entree! We have orange chicken and Teriyaki chicken, too!

attending_trucks.name: Hungry Hawaiian
attending_trucks.about: The Hungry Hawaiian is a rebirth of my father's restaurant that was originally opened in 1978. We launched our restaurant in June 2017 and the food truck February 2018. Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

attending_trucks.name: Family Squeezed Lemonade
attending_trucks.about: Our fresh ingredients are chopped, sliced & smashed right before your eyes.  Nothing from mix or concentrate.  Throw in a little sugar, some ice & water, and your beverage is ready for you. It’s easy to like lemonade, it’s easier to LOVE award-winning Family Squeezed Lemonade!

attending_trucks.name: Fiore Pizza
attending_trucks.about: We are a mobile pizzeria creating handmade Italian style pizzas using fresh local ingredients. Pizzas are prepared and baked on-site in our Neapolitan wood-fired brick oven.

attending_trucks.name: Smoke a Billy BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Inspired by Rock a Billy and the best smoked and cooked meats around.  Our passion for authentic homestyle and original BBQ keeps us striving for the very best.  All of our entrees are made fresh to order - freshness & satisfaction guaranteed!

attending_trucks.name: Apollo Truck
attending_trucks.about: We char-broil our burgers to order, serve only the most delicious french fries we could find, compose our salads on the spot, and offer our own signature sandwiches, desserts, sauces and salad dressings. Add fresh lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and our homemade Apollo sauce to your burger with a lightly toasted, cornmeal bun.

attending_trucks.name: Cluck Truck
attending_trucks.about: Do you love fried chicken? So do we! We serve fresh, delicious fried chicken wraps in a variety of tasty styles. Try the Original, a mango chipotle slaw with a honey chili drizzle or Greek, Hawaiian, Chinese or BBQ flavors!  Add a side of garlic parmesan fries for a real feast!All things Chicken! Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

attending_trucks.name: San Diablo Artisan Churros
attending_trucks.about: Our artisan churros are made from scratch, deep-fried fresh on-demand to golden perfection, coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon and then filled with your choice of sweet decadence like dulce de leche, nutella, sweet cream or seasonal (piña colada, strawberry lemonade, coconut cream, pumpkin cheesecake, caramel apple etc) and customized filling flavors and colors (to match whatever theme you have).

attending_trucks.name: Porteña Gourmet Empanadas
attending_trucks.about: Flavors of home at your fingertips! Gourmet, fresh baked Argentinian empanadas.  We use a wide variety of flavors & textures, our empanadas are made with fresh seasonal ingredients that can satisfy your savory and sweet cravings.Porteña is proud to offer empanadas, a pastry pocket stuffed with a filling of your choice, that are meant to be shared around the table with your loved ones. We don't just feed people - we nourish them.

attending_trucks.name: Jurassic Street Tacos
attending_trucks.about: Jurassic Tacos started by us selling tacos from the back of a truck, to now having two trailers to feed the Jurassic size hunger of Salt Lake City and Utah. Our goal at Jurassic Street Tacos is to make sure the tacos you eat from us are the most delicious, biggest, and most talked about in the state of Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Thirs-T Specialty Drinks and Edible Cookie Dough
attending_trucks.about: You can order a refreshing fountain drink and customize it with our menu of 20+ syrup flavors. Thirs-T also has edible cookie dough thats ready to eat. Choose from our rotating menu of flavors.

attending_trucks.name: Kia Ora Kiwi

attending_trucks.about: We serve a variety of gourmet toasted cheese sandwiches and fresh cut fries.  We use premium and fresh ingredients which stand out from the crowd.  If you love cheese, you will love us! Premium toasted cheese sandwich and fresh cut fries.

attending_trucks.name: Noemi’s Catering
attending_trucks.about: Noemi's catering is an company that started from catering and now it has grown in to the food truck world. Noemi the owner/chef brings her Chilean food style to Utah. Noemi's experience comes from growing up in the countryside of Chile, learning how to cook and bake. When Noemi got older she opened up a bakery and ran it with her family. Later, Noemi moved to the USA. She was the head cook for the Chilean Community for many years. Now she is growing into the food truck world and wants to share with you the flavors of Chile.

attending_trucks.name: Slice-A-Pizza
attending_trucks.about: Traditional 1980's American Pizzeria-style take on pizza, made to order. Not gourmet & not wood-fired. Choose from our infamous Cheese Bread, BBQ Chicken Pizza or Pizza Pocket. Ask about our Gluten-free/ Keto crust option that everyone's raving about!

Maple bacon, Nutella banana, caramel apple, and cookies n cream!

We hope you grow to love Peruvian food as much as we do and hope that it opens doors to exploring the beautiful culture that Peru holds.Come try our delicious empanadas which come in meat and vegetarian options or any of our other Peruvian specialties!

attending_trucks.name: Falafel Tree
attending_trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Crunchy Munchy Lumpia

Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

attending_trucks.name: Annie's Crepes & Cakes
attending_trucks.about: Our crepes come in a variety of flavors in both sweet and savory categories. Wanting something different? Try one of our unique bubble waffles!

attending_trucks.name: Slice-A-Pizza
attending_trucks.about: Traditional 1980's American Pizzeria-style take on pizza, made to order. Not gourmet & not wood-fired. Choose from our infamous Cheese Bread, BBQ Chicken Pizza or Pizza Pocket. Ask about our Gluten-free/ Keto crust option that everyone's raving about!

attending_trucks.name: Comfort Bowl
attending_trucks.about: Just what it says . . . comfort food in a bowl! You’ll love their Japanese-style fried chicken and veggies covered with a sweet & spicy sauce. All of their bowls come included with lemongrass steamed rice and a Thai salad. Toss a few spring rolls on the side - you are sure to walk away pleased!Be sure to try their chicken katsu, which is their best seller. You won't be disappointed!

attending_trucks.name: South of the Border Tacos
attending_trucks.about: Delicious Mexican food! Try our burritos, tacos, tortas, quesadillas, or especially our supreme nachos! Everything is fresh made from scratch!

attending_trucks.name: Kona Ice
attending_trucks.about: | Kona Ice is premium tropical shaved ice made with quality ingredients and stevia. We offer delicious crafted flavors with ice-cream and cream.🍧If you are looking for the perfect summer treat Kona ice caters all types of events - corporate, festival, schools, sports and much more! Kona Ice operates a one of a kind mobile truck 🚚 a Kiosk 🚙, sure to make a lasting impression and an indoor unit.

events.name: Murray Takeout Night
events.description: Don't fight over what to cook or where to eat! We're taking over the stress of dinner on Tuesday nights! Come get something everyone will enjoy while you relax and enjoy the evening, every Tuesday night through the season!
events.address: Murray Park, 272 E Murray Park Ave

attending_trucks.name: Yoshi's Enso Grill
attending_trucks.about: Yoshi's Enso Grill is the food truck version of the popular Yoshi's Japanese Grill in Salt Lake City.  😀  We have sweet and spicy flavors in our rice bowls, sushi, egg rolls and more! We're sure we have something you will enjoy!

attending_trucks.name: Smokin Star BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Welcome to the meat mecca of Smokin Star BBQ, which has perfected the art of slow cooked meats using the most flavorful, aromatic, perfectly seasoned cherry & pecan hardwood and self taught recipes. Our heaping platters or meat by the pound includes several daily meat choices as well as holiday specials. Our goal is to Serve bbq that gives one a foodgasmic experience!

attending_trucks.name: Clark's Malasadas
attending_trucks.about: A malasada is a Portuguese donut, without a hole, that was made popular by Hawaii. You can find them everywhere in Hawaii, but they aren't as common here in Utah! The malasadas that we make will all be rolled in either sugar, or cinnamon and sugar. You can also have them filled with different flavors of custards and creams.

attending_trucks.name: Bruges
attending_trucks.about: Since 2004, Bruges shares the best loved foods from Belgium with Utah. Their food is not only fun, but it is authentic, artisan made with natural ingredients and prepared fresh for you. Try their unique sweet caramelized Liège waffle, award winning fries (frites) or famous Machine Gun Sandwich. Experience true Belgian indulgence without the jetlag.

attending_trucks.name: Falafel Tree
attending_trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Cluck Truck
attending_trucks.about: Do you love fried chicken? So do we! We serve fresh, delicious fried chicken wraps in a variety of tasty styles. Try the Original, a mango chipotle slaw with a honey chili drizzle or Greek, Hawaiian, Chinese or BBQ flavors!  Add a side of garlic parmesan fries for a real feast!All things Chicken! Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

attending_trucks.name: Apollo Truck
attending_trucks.about: We char-broil our burgers to order, serve only the most delicious french fries we could find, compose our salads on the spot, and offer our own signature sandwiches, desserts, sauces and salad dressings. Add fresh lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and our homemade Apollo sauce to your burger with a lightly toasted, cornmeal bun.

Come try our delicious ramen options of Tonkotsu Ramen, Shoyu Ramen, or Miso Ramen. Each have their own unique flavor for you to enjoy. We also serve the ever-popular sushi rolls such as the California roll, Vegas roll, and others!

attending_trucks.name: Wings on Wheels
attending_trucks.about: A food truck/catering business with great customer service that is dedicated to serving fresh and delicious food. Our delicious wings are served with homemade sauces that will make your taste buds fall in love. Come and enjoy! We cater. Ask for the menu.

attending_trucks.name: Sobe eats
attending_trucks.about: Sobe eats culinary concepts is a sustainable, environmentally friendly and plant forward company with strong family and community values. Found by 3 brothers and accomplished professional local chefs with a strong passion. Hungry to share our culture and experience thru our 25+ culinary journey.

attending_trucks.about: We are a mobile pizzeria creating handmade Italian style pizzas using fresh local ingredients. Pizzas are prepared and baked on-site in our Neapolitan wood-fired brick oven.

Try our Raspberry Cheesecake scone with our refreshing flavored iced milk in the Summer or in the Winter a hot Cookie Butter Fudge scone with a gourmet flavored hot chocolate.

attending_trucks.name: Hunt's Texas BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Texas Flavor on the go! Try our sliced brisket tender smoked low and slow, our pork riblets of three flavors, or our juicy and bold chicken quarter. Order with a side of South Texas style pinto beans or seasoned kernel's bacon fried corn, then finish with our frito pie and you've got a true Texas meal!

attending_trucks.name: Rimmels
attending_trucks.about: Rimmels was started by three German Brothers, they however decided that they missed home and wanted to move back. So they sold Rimmels to the James Ewell and me, his daughter, McKenzie Palmer. I went to culinary school and always wanted to run my own business in the food industry.. James always wanted to run his own business as well. We purchased Rimmels in May 2019. We are so excited and we plan to stick to the Rimmel’s roots and stay with the authentic German taste! We love to serve people great food and make their experience enjoyable!

attending_trucks.name: San Diablo Artisan Churros
attending_trucks.about: Our artisan churros are made from scratch, deep-fried fresh on-demand to golden perfection, coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon and then filled with your choice of sweet decadence like dulce de leche, nutella, sweet cream or seasonal (piña colada, strawberry lemonade, coconut cream, pumpkin cheesecake, caramel apple etc) and customized filling flavors and colors (to match whatever theme you have).

attending_trucks.about: Born in the Philippines and raised in Maui, Hawaii, our creator put the two best foods together and brought it to Utah as Dakine Grindz - Hawaiian fare that includes a taste of the Philippines! Try our delicious kabobs or kalua pork; or our Filipino favorites like lumpia, pancit or pork adobo!

attending_trucks.name: Bomb Dilla
attending_trucks.about: Bombdilla is a LA flair food truck. We specialize on loaded quesadilla and loaded tater tots! We promise you Utah it's going to be the BOMB!

attending_trucks.name: Bruges
attending_trucks.about: Since 2004, Bruges shares the best loved foods from Belgium with Utah. Their food is not only fun, but it is authentic, artisan made with natural ingredients and prepared fresh for you. Try their unique sweet caramelized Liège waffle, award winning fries (frites) or famous Machine Gun Sandwich. Experience true Belgian indulgence without the jetlag.

attending_trucks.name: Falafel Tree
attending_trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Black’s Sliders
attending_trucks.about: Our food is hormone and antibiotic free and purchased from Wasatch meats , a local  vendor who holds the same vision of health through product excellence. We serve a variety of sliders and fries that everyone will love! Enjoy a choice of beef, chicken, pork or vegetarian sliders with toppings like cheddar cheese, caramelized onions & an array of fresh vegetables!  Don’t forget a side of our amazing, uniquely flavored fries!

attending_trucks.name: San Diablo Artisan Churros
attending_trucks.about: Our artisan churros are made from scratch, deep-fried fresh on-demand to golden perfection, coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon and then filled with your choice of sweet decadence like dulce de leche, nutella, sweet cream or seasonal (piña colada, strawberry lemonade, coconut cream, pumpkin cheesecake, caramel apple etc) and customized filling flavors and colors (to match whatever theme you have).

attending_trucks.name: Cool Treats
attending_trucks.about: Try our delicious, creamy, and tasty ice cream treats.  With everything from cones, sundaes, shakes, and floats we can satisfy whatever your ice cream craving is!  Cool Treats is the place to get the coolest treats in town and cool off in the HOT sun.

attending_trucks.name: Mamas mobile toasted cheeser
attending_trucks.about: We serve a variety of gourmet toasted cheese sandwiches and fresh cut fries.  We use premium and fresh ingredients which stand out from the crowd.  If you love cheese, you will love us! Premium toasted cheese sandwich and fresh cut fries.

attending_trucks.name: Pizza Cone Zone
attending_trucks.about: Golden Pizza Dough in the shape of a cone, stuffed with  the highest quality meats and cheeses - baked on site to perfection. So unique, so different, so delicious • You really can put Pizza in a Cone!!

Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

attending_trucks.name: Papito Moes Puerto Rican Grub
attending_trucks.about: Papito Moe's is bringing Puerto Rican Flavor to Utah! We’ve come to Utah hungry to share traditional island favorites with you...Can you say Pernil, Mofongo, Tostones Empanadillas, and more?! Come Savor the Taste of the Island and put some WEPA in your step!

attending_trucks.name: Bruges
attending_trucks.about: Since 2004, Bruges shares the best loved foods from Belgium with Utah. Their food is not only fun, but it is authentic, artisan made with natural ingredients and prepared fresh for you. Try their unique sweet caramelized Liège waffle, award winning fries (frites) or famous Machine Gun Sandwich. Experience true Belgian indulgence without the jetlag.

events.name: Bruges
events.description: Sharing the joy of Belgium's best loved foods

attending_trucks.name: El Sarten Italian Pasta
attending_trucks.about: We offer a variety of Italian Pasta, homemade sauces and many toppings. We specialize in combining your likes into your pasta. You choose your pasta, sauce, and toppings. Then our International chef will create an amazing combination just for you. Your perfect pasta!

attending_trucks.name: Hungry Hawaiian
attending_trucks.about: The Hungry Hawaiian is a rebirth of my father's restaurant that was originally opened in 1978. We launched our restaurant in June 2017 and the food truck February 2018. Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

attending_trucks.about: One of a kind! we have mixed soda, grilled cheese, soft pretzels and more! all at a price that won’t break the bank! Try our pulled pork grilled cheese!

attending_trucks.name: J.Dawgs
attending_trucks.about: Nearly 20 years ago I pawned my Fender Telecaster to rebuild a small red shack in a small town with a few simple ideas: that food should be simple, that tin foil is better than plates and that napkins are always optional. That shack became my favorite place on earth, where a hot grill, all-natural dawgs, and homemade buns served over a good conversation are always an man's best friend. Now we are bringing the shack to you.  Enjoy!-J

attending_trucks.name: Shylo's Mobile Cafe
attending_trucks.about: Shylo’s Mobile Café is an amazing food truck that serves fresh and hearty artisan sandwiches, soups, fries and pies.  Shylo’s Mobile Café has the food truck industry by storm! We create a synergy of creative, quick, addicting dishes from our executive chef!

attending_trucks.name: Udder Rivals
attending_trucks.about:
Udder Rivals ice cream carries 12 delicious flavors of scooped ice cream from BYU and USU creameries available in cups or on cones! The rivalry comes from the national collegiate ice cream competition each June. BYU and USU rank in the top 13 every year! Take the Udder Challenge and decide which creamery is your favorite!

With the ice cream of your dreams, Udder Rivals food truck is serving Utah scooped ice cream, sundaes, floats and cookies from both BYU and USU creameries!Try the Udder Challenge, a scoop of vanilla from each school, and vote for your favorite!

events.name: Millcreek Takeout Night
events.description: Don't fight over what to cook or where to eat! We're taking over the stress of dinner on Thursday nights! Come get something everyone will enjoy while you relax and enjoy the evening, every Thursday night through the season!

attending_trucks.name: Mamas mobile toasted cheeser
attending_trucks.about: We serve a variety of gourmet toasted cheese sandwiches and fresh cut fries.  We use premium and fresh ingredients which stand out from the crowd.  If you love cheese, you will love us! Premium toasted cheese sandwich and fresh cut fries.

attending_trucks.name: DaKine Grindz
attending_trucks.about: Born in the Philippines and raised in Maui, Hawaii, our creator put the two best foods together and brought it to Utah as Dakine Grindz - Hawaiian fare that includes a taste of the Philippines! Try our delicious kabobs or kalua pork; or our Filipino favorites like lumpia, pancit or pork adobo!

attending_trucks.name: Family Squeezed Lemonade
attending_trucks.about: Our fresh ingredients are chopped, sliced & smashed right before your eyes.  Nothing from mix or concentrate.  Throw in a little sugar, some ice & water, and your beverage is ready for you. It’s easy to like lemonade, it’s easier to LOVE award-winning Family Squeezed Lemonade!

attending_trucks.name: Red Beard BBQ
attending_trucks.about: We spin a Western attitude on traditional Southern Smokehouse BBQ! In addition to our best-in-the-west slow smoked pork and brisket, we smoke burgers, dogs and sausages with some wild combinations! True to our name, you'll want more of our house-made sauces sure to require a napkin! You'll love our sides, sizable portions and wide variety of options including salads and desserts. Come wipe your face with us!

attending_trucks.name: Churrology
attending_trucks.about: Our churros are made from scratch! Top with chocolate, strawberry, caramel, or sweet icing - we know everybody has their favorite! You can also try our Churro Tots - each order comes with a choice of 2 or 4 dipping flavors. Also available for private events, parties and corporate bookings.

attending_trucks.about: We were Trained to make Philly Style Cheesesteaks from Jim's on South Street in Philly. We hold true to what we were taught and of course we believe we are the best in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: The Daily Shave Ice
attending_trucks.about: Local fresh shave ice!

attending_trucks.name: Slice-A-Pizza
attending_trucks.about: Traditional 1980's American Pizzeria-style take on pizza, made to order. Not gourmet & not wood-fired. Choose from our infamous Cheese Bread, BBQ Chicken Pizza or Pizza Pocket. Ask about our Gluten-free/ Keto crust option that everyone's raving about!

attending_trucks.name: Falafel Tree
attending_trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Kolache Krave
attending_trucks.about:
Kolache would be the last product you would expect from a software developer and engineer. After learning some culinary chemistry and going through hundreds of pounds of different flours, unique oils and, various concoctions to develop our Kolache dough. The dough we developed is what we call an American Kolache, which is a soft pillowy sweet bread that can encapsulate just about anything sweet or savory. We hope you love them!
Our delicious Kolache is slightly sweet, dough stuffed with the best fresh ingredients. Hand stuffed every morning using our unique dough recipe. Our Kolache is perfect for breakfast and lunch or even your late-night cravings.
