attending_trucks.name: Where's Aldo? Taqueria
attending_trucks.about: Where's Aldo? is a mobile taqueria bring QUICK, AUTHENTIC, and DELICIOUS street tacos and more to locations all over the Wasatch Front.  Aldo brings his favorite family recipes from Mérida, the vibrant capital of the Mexican state of Yucatán.  Each specialty meat is marinated overnight, cooked to perfection, and topped with fresh homemade salsas.  Complete your meal with a bottled Mexican soda and fried ice cream for dessert.

attending_trucks.name: Yoshi's Enso Grill
attending_trucks.about: Yoshi's Enso Grill is the food truck version of the popular Yoshi's Japanese Grill in Salt Lake City.  😀  We have sweet and spicy flavors in our rice bowls, sushi, egg rolls and more! We're sure we have something you will enjoy!

attending_trucks.name: CupBop
attending_trucks.about: 'CUPBOP' is a new trend in Korean style take-out food. Korean BBQ in a cup! CupBop uses an amazing blend of spices & sauces to top your choice of rice, noodles, vegetables, pork, chicken or beef! Choose hot & spicy or sweet & tangy! Indulge in this Korean BBQ layered with pure goodness! Korean style veggie noodles with rice and a seasonal menu are also available.

attending_trucks.name: The Salty Pineapple
attending_trucks.about: We are a Hawaiian style BBQ food truck located in Salt Lake City, UT. Bringing the Big Island taste we all love to the mainland! Our sweet garlic chicken and mouth watering pork sliders are just a hint of what we bring to the table!

attending_trucks.name: Bomb Dilla
attending_trucks.about: Bombdilla is a LA flair food truck. We specialize on loaded quesadilla and loaded tater tots! We promise you Utah it's going to be the BOMB!

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

attending_trucks.name: Family Squeezed Lemonade
attending_trucks.about: Our fresh ingredients are chopped, sliced & smashed right before your eyes.  Nothing from mix or concentrate.  Throw in a little sugar, some ice & water, and your beverage is ready for you. It’s easy to like lemonade, it’s easier to LOVE award-winning Family Squeezed Lemonade!

attending_trucks.name: San Diablo Artisan Churros
attending_trucks.about: Our artisan churros are made from scratch, deep-fried fresh on-demand to golden perfection, coated with sugar and freshly-ground cinnamon and then filled with your choice of sweet decadence like dulce de leche, nutella, sweet cream or seasonal (piña colada, strawberry lemonade, coconut cream, pumpkin cheesecake, caramel apple etc) and customized filling flavors and colors (to match whatever theme you have).

events.name: Bountiful Takeout Night
events.description: Don't fight over what to cook or where to eat! We're taking over the stress of dinner on Friday nights! Come get something everyone will enjoy while you relax and enjoy the evening, every Friday night through the season!

attending_trucks.name: Mamas mobile toasted cheeser
attending_trucks.about: We serve a variety of gourmet toasted cheese sandwiches and fresh cut fries.  We use premium and fresh ingredients which stand out from the crowd.  If you love cheese, you will love us! Premium toasted cheese sandwich and fresh cut fries.

attending_trucks.name: Smokin Star BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Welcome to the meat mecca of Smokin Star BBQ, which has perfected the art of slow cooked meats using the most flavorful, aromatic, perfectly seasoned cherry & pecan hardwood and self taught recipes. Our heaping platters or meat by the pound includes several daily meat choices as well as holiday specials. Our goal is to Serve bbq that gives one a foodgasmic experience!

attending_trucks.name: DaKine Grindz
attending_trucks.about: Born in the Philippines and raised in Maui, Hawaii, our creator put the two best foods together and brought it to Utah as Dakine Grindz - Hawaiian fare that includes a taste of the Philippines! Try our delicious kabobs or kalua pork; or our Filipino favorites like lumpia, pancit or pork adobo!

attending_trucks.name: Marquesas Corndogs
attending_trucks.about: Named after the television show Survivor Marquesas, these are a not your mama's frozen corndogs! We serve hand-dipped golden delicious corndogs, double-hand  battered dill pickle spears, tillamook cheese sticks and sweet fried candy bars.

attending_trucks.name: Black’s Sliders
attending_trucks.about: Our food is hormone and antibiotic free and purchased from Wasatch meats , a local  vendor who holds the same vision of health through product excellence. We serve a variety of sliders and fries that everyone will love! Enjoy a choice of beef, chicken, pork or vegetarian sliders with toppings like cheddar cheese, caramelized onions & an array of fresh vegetables!  Don’t forget a side of our amazing, uniquely flavored fries!

attending_trucks.name: The Red Food Truck
attending_trucks.about: Delicious Peruvian-style sandwiches filled with savory meats & fresh veggies. Try our popular Lomo Saltado Sandwich. We start with a soft ciabatta roll loaded with grilled steak, peppers, onions and a special sauce that sets it apart from any sandwich you have ever had!

attending_trucks.name: Cool Treats
attending_trucks.about: Try our delicious, creamy, and tasty ice cream treats.  With everything from cones, sundaes, shakes, and floats we can satisfy whatever your ice cream craving is!  Cool Treats is the place to get the coolest treats in town and cool off in the HOT sun.

attending_trucks.name: Cluck Truck
attending_trucks.about: Do you love fried chicken? So do we! We serve fresh, delicious fried chicken wraps in a variety of tasty styles. Try the Original, a mango chipotle slaw with a honey chili drizzle or Greek, Hawaiian, Chinese or BBQ flavors!  Add a side of garlic parmesan fries for a real feast!All things Chicken! Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

attending_trucks.name: Fiore Pizza
attending_trucks.about: We are a mobile pizzeria creating handmade Italian style pizzas using fresh local ingredients. Pizzas are prepared and baked on-site in our Neapolitan wood-fired brick oven.

His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

Signature sauces compliment our sweet items and they are always topped with fresh berries and house whipped cream.

attending_trucks.name: The Red Food Truck
attending_trucks.about: Delicious Peruvian-style sandwiches filled with savory meats & fresh veggies. Try our popular Lomo Saltado Sandwich. We start with a soft ciabatta roll loaded with grilled steak, peppers, onions and a special sauce that sets it apart from any sandwich you have ever had!

attending_trucks.name: Falafel Tree
attending_trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Smokin Star BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Welcome to the meat mecca of Smokin Star BBQ, which has perfected the art of slow cooked meats using the most flavorful, aromatic, perfectly seasoned cherry & pecan hardwood and self taught recipes. Our heaping platters or meat by the pound includes several daily meat choices as well as holiday specials. Our goal is to Serve bbq that gives one a foodgasmic experience!

attending_trucks.name: Clark's Malasadas
attending_trucks.about: A malasada is a Portuguese donut, without a hole, that was made popular by Hawaii. You can find them everywhere in Hawaii, but they aren't as common here in Utah! The malasadas that we make will all be rolled in either sugar, or cinnamon and sugar. You can also have them filled with different flavors of custards and creams.

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

attending_trucks.name: Jurassic Street Tacos
attending_trucks.about: Jurassic Tacos started by us selling tacos from the back of a truck, to now having two trailers to feed the Jurassic size hunger of Salt Lake City and Utah. Our goal at Jurassic Street Tacos is to make sure the tacos you eat from us are the most delicious, biggest, and most talked about in the state of Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Apollo Truck
attending_trucks.about: We char-broil our burgers to order, serve only the most delicious french fries we could find, compose our salads on the spot, and offer our own signature sandwiches, desserts, sauces and salad dressings. Add fresh lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and our homemade Apollo sauce to your burger with a lightly toasted, cornmeal bun.

attending_trucks.name: Cluck Truck
attending_trucks.about: Do you love fried chicken? So do we! We serve fresh, delicious fried chicken wraps in a variety of tasty styles. Try the Original, a mango chipotle slaw with a honey chili drizzle or Greek, Hawaiian, Chinese or BBQ flavors!  Add a side of garlic parmesan fries for a real feast!All things Chicken! Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

events.description: Don't fight over what to cook or where to eat! We're taking over the stress of dinner on Tuesday nights! Come get something everyone will enjoy while you relax and enjoy the evening, every Tuesday night through the season!
events.address: Murray Park, 272 E Murray Park Ave

attending_trucks.name: The Salty Pineapple
attending_trucks.about: We are a Hawaiian style BBQ food truck located in Salt Lake City, UT. Bringing the Big Island taste we all love to the mainland! Our sweet garlic chicken and mouth watering pork sliders are just a hint of what we bring to the table!

attending_trucks.name: Papito Moes Puerto Rican Grub
attending_trucks.about: Papito Moe's is bringing Puerto Rican Flavor to Utah! We’ve come to Utah hungry to share traditional island favorites with you...Can you say Pernil, Mofongo, Tostones Empanadillas, and more?! Come Savor the Taste of the Island and put some WEPA in your step!

attending_trucks.name: Bruges
attending_trucks.about: Since 2004, Bruges shares the best loved foods from Belgium with Utah. Their food is not only fun, but it is authentic, artisan made with natural ingredients and prepared fresh for you. Try their unique sweet caramelized Liège waffle, award winning fries (frites) or famous Machine Gun Sandwich. Experience true Belgian indulgence without the jetlag.

attending_trucks.name: Porteña Gourmet Empanadas
attending_trucks.about: Flavors of home at your fingertips! Gourmet, fresh baked Argentinian empanadas.  We use a wide variety of flavors & textures, our empanadas are made with fresh seasonal ingredients that can satisfy your savory and sweet cravings.Porteña is proud to offer empanadas, a pastry pocket stuffed with a filling of your choice, that are meant to be shared around the table with your loved ones. We don't just feed people - we nourish them.

attending_trucks.name: Churrology
attending_trucks.about: Our churros are made from scratch! Top with chocolate, strawberry, caramel, or sweet icing - we know everybody has their favorite! You can also try our Churro Tots - each order comes with a choice of 2 or 4 dipping flavors. Also available for private events, parties and corporate bookings.

attending_trucks.name: Sobe eats
attending_trucks.about: Sobe eats culinary concepts is a sustainable, environmentally friendly and plant forward company with strong family and community values. Found by 3 brothers and accomplished professional local chefs with a strong passion. Hungry to share our culture and experience thru our 25+ culinary journey.

attending_trucks.name: Shylo's Mobile Cafe
attending_trucks.about: Shylo’s Mobile Café is an amazing food truck that serves fresh and hearty artisan sandwiches, soups, fries and pies.  Shylo’s Mobile Café has the food truck industry by storm! We create a synergy of creative, quick, addicting dishes from our executive chef!

attending_trucks.about: Inspired by Rock a Billy and the best smoked and cooked meats around.  Our passion for authentic homestyle and original BBQ keeps us striving for the very best.  All of our entrees are made fresh to order - freshness & satisfaction guaranteed!

attending_trucks.name: Comfort Bowl
attending_trucks.about: Just what it says . . . comfort food in a bowl! You’ll love their Japanese-style fried chicken and veggies covered with a sweet & spicy sauce. All of their bowls come included with lemongrass steamed rice and a Thai salad. Toss a few spring rolls on the side - you are sure to walk away pleased!Be sure to try their chicken katsu, which is their best seller. You won't be disappointed!

attending_trucks.name: The Ramen
attending_trucks.about: Our menu features 5 main ramen dishes built upon a yummy broth soup. Spice it up or add some soy sauce for a terrific flavor. Top it off with sprouts, green onions, boiled egg, corn & a slice of pork roast!

attending_trucks.name: Black’s Sliders
attending_trucks.about: Our food is hormone and antibiotic free and purchased from Wasatch meats , a local  vendor who holds the same vision of health through product excellence. We serve a variety of sliders and fries that everyone will love! Enjoy a choice of beef, chicken, pork or vegetarian sliders with toppings like cheddar cheese, caramelized onions & an array of fresh vegetables!  Don’t forget a side of our amazing, uniquely flavored fries!

We hope you grow to love Peruvian food as much as we do and hope that it opens doors to exploring the beautiful culture that Peru holds.Come try our delicious empanadas which come in meat and vegetarian options or any of our other Peruvian specialties!

attending_trucks.name: Fatty Tuna Food
attending_trucks.about: Fatty Tuna food truck thrives on presenting our customers with tasteful authentic sushi and ramen through texture, spices, local produce and fresh fish. Come try our delicious ramen options of Tonkotsu Ramen, Shoyu Ramen, or Miso Ramen. Each have their own unique flavor for you to enjoy. We also serve the ever-popular sushi rolls such as the California roll, Vegas roll, and others!

My husband and the owner of the truck loves to cook. He has been chef at different places around US for over 20 years.

attending_trucks.name: DaKine Grindz
attending_trucks.about: Born in the Philippines and raised in Maui, Hawaii, our creator put the two best foods together and brought it to Utah as Dakine Grindz - Hawaiian fare that includes a taste of the Philippines! Try our delicious kabobs or kalua pork; or our Filipino favorites like lumpia, pancit or pork adobo!

attending_trucks.name: Kolache Krave
attending_trucks.about:
Kolache would be the last product you would expect from a software developer and engineer. After learning some culinary chemistry and going through hundreds of pounds of different flours, unique oils and, various concoctions to develop our Kolache dough. The dough we developed is what we call an American Kolache, which is a soft pillowy sweet bread that can encapsulate just about anything sweet or savory. We hope you love them!
Our delicious Kolache is slightly sweet, dough stuffed with the best fresh ingredients. Hand stuffed every morning using our unique dough recipe. Our Kolache is perfect for breakfast and lunch or even your late-night cravings.

attending_trucks.about: Specialty hand-dipped corndogs!  You can't top our all beef dog breaded in a deliciously thick, sweet and crispy cornmeal layer. Be sure to add a side of waffle fries - they’re seasoned to  crispy perfection!

attending_trucks.name: District Thai Fusion
attending_trucks.about: "Thai so nice, you'll want to come back twice!" We serve up all the exotic flavors of authentic Thai food in traditional dishes to treat your tastebuds to a world of flavor. Start with an egg roll or a pork dumpling, then try one of our delectable curries or a pad thai entree! We have orange chicken and Teriyaki chicken, too!

attending_trucks.name: Sconey Island
attending_trucks.about: Delicious hot fried bread with gourmet toppings served with gourmet flavored iced drinks in the summer and hot in the winter. Sitting around the dinner table of their rundown college dorm, they dreamed up the idea of bringing bingsu to Utah. With the help of fellow owners Tate Hicken and Marsha Wallin, In summer of 2020, Bing's Korean Desserts became a reality.

None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Fiore Pizza
attending_trucks.about: We are a mobile pizzeria creating handmade Italian style pizzas using fresh local ingredients. Pizzas are prepared and baked on-site in our Neapolitan wood-fired brick oven.

attending_trucks.about: Texas Flavor on the go! Try our sliced brisket tender smoked low and slow, our pork riblets of three flavors, or our juicy and bold chicken quarter. Order with a side of South Texas style pinto beans or seasoned kernel's bacon fried corn, then finish with our frito pie and you've got a true Texas meal!

attending_trucks.name: Fatty Tuna Food
attending_trucks.about: Fatty Tuna food truck thrives on presenting our customers with tasteful authentic sushi and ramen through texture, spices, local produce and fresh fish. Come try our delicious ramen options of Tonkotsu Ramen, Shoyu Ramen, or Miso Ramen. Each have their own unique flavor for you to enjoy. We also serve the ever-popular sushi rolls such as the California roll, Vegas roll, and others!

attending_trucks.name: Family Squeezed Lemonade
attending_trucks.about: Our fresh ingredients are chopped, sliced & smashed right before your eyes.  Nothing from mix or concentrate.  Throw in a little sugar, some ice & water, and your beverage is ready for you. It’s easy to like lemonade, it’s easier to LOVE award-winning Family Squeezed Lemonade!

attending_trucks.name: Utah Killer Dogs llc
attending_trucks.about: Our open flamed grilled Hot Dogs are 100% beef.  Our Killer sauce is sweet and spicy, & is the perfect complement to this spectacular Dog! Add a bag of crisp chips & an ice cold drink and you have the perfect meal.

attending_trucks.name: Shylo's Mobile Cafe
attending_trucks.about: Shylo’s Mobile Café is an amazing food truck that serves fresh and hearty artisan sandwiches, soups, fries and pies.  Shylo’s Mobile Café has the food truck industry by storm! We create a synergy of creative, quick, addicting dishes from our executive chef!

attending_trucks.name: Sobe eats

attending_trucks.name: Hungry Hawaiian
attending_trucks.about: The Hungry Hawaiian is a rebirth of my father's restaurant that was originally opened in 1978. We launched our restaurant in June 2017 and the food truck February 2018. Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

Our heaping platters or meat by the pound includes several daily meat choices as well as holiday specials. Our goal is to Serve bbq that gives one a foodgasmic experience!

attending_trucks.name: Rimmels
attending_trucks.about: Rimmels was started by three German Brothers, they however decided that they missed home and wanted to move back. So they sold Rimmels to the James Ewell and me, his daughter, McKenzie Palmer. I went to culinary school and always wanted to run my own business in the food industry.. James always wanted to run his own business as well. We purchased Rimmels in May 2019. We are so excited and we plan to stick to the Rimmel’s roots and stay with the authentic German taste! We love to serve people great food and make their experience enjoyable!

attending_trucks.name: The Pizza Bus
attending_trucks.about: Pizza is always a good answer! The Pizza Bus offers quality food, great service, and fair prices. This truck can cater anything from wedding parties to family reunions. Book them for your next office lunch or midnight softball tournament. You absolutely cannot go wrong with a Classic Pepperoni or Triple Cheese pizza - and you’ll love the specialty pizzas like Chicken Bacon BBQ or Spicy Luau.  Be sure to snap a picture in front of the Pizza Bus, and ask owner Dave for a tour when it’s slow :)

attending_trucks.name: Freshies Lobster Co
attending_trucks.about: It started with two  New Englanders selling lobster rolls out of a 10x10 tent 10 years ago in Park City, they now have a restaurant and food truck in the Park City and Salt Lake area.  They are know for their very authentic and delicious Lobster Roll.  They do this by shipping in the lobster fresh from the shores of Maine and the bread is shipped from Maine as well.  Try our perfected, traditional, New England style fresh lobster roll (voted “World’s Best Lobster Roll” at the “Down East Lobster Roll Festival” competition in Portland, Maine!), lobster sliders, salads and more.

attending_trucks.name: Churrology

Our menu features traditional dishes and southern cuisine along with a few of our own creations and twists on the classics. If you're looking to experience authentic local food, served in a casual and friendly atmosphere, come visit our Food Truck today.

attending_trucks.name: Traditions Mobile Cafe

attending_trucks.name: Kolache Krave
attending_trucks.about:
Kolache would be the last product you would expect from a software developer and engineer. After learning some culinary chemistry and going through hundreds of pounds of different flours, unique oils and, various concoctions to develop our Kolache dough. The dough we developed is what we call an American Kolache, which is a soft pillowy sweet bread that can encapsulate just about anything sweet or savory. We hope you love them!
Our delicious Kolache is slightly sweet, dough stuffed with the best fresh ingredients. Hand stuffed every morning using our unique dough recipe. Our Kolache is perfect for breakfast and lunch or even your late-night cravings.

attending_trucks.about: Just what it says . . . comfort food in a bowl! You’ll love their Japanese-style fried chicken and veggies covered with a sweet & spicy sauce. All of their bowls come included with lemongrass steamed rice and a Thai salad. Toss a few spring rolls on the side - you are sure to walk away pleased!Be sure to try their chicken katsu, which is their best seller. You won't be disappointed!

attending_trucks.name: Crunchy Munchy Lumpia
attending_trucks.about: Crunchy Munchy is famous in Filipino Lumpia also know as Eggroll. With its unique taste, you'll be able to identify the freshness of its ingredients. We have the meat rolls and vegetable rolls. Also, we have some signature desserts you'll love

attending_trucks.name: Shrimp Shak
attending_trucks.about: Enjoy our freshly beer battered shrimp with our homemade cocktail sauce and amazing waffle fries.

events.description: Don't fight over what to cook or where to eat! We're taking over the stress of dinner on Thursday nights! Come get something everyone will enjoy while you relax and enjoy the evening, every Thursday night through the season!

attending_trucks.name: El Sarten Mexicano
attending_trucks.about:
At El Sarten Food Truck, we take great pride in carefully preparing each meal by hand and made with love using authentic family recipes passed down from one generation to the next. It doesn't matter who you are, or where you're from, when you come to our restaurant, we treat you like family. 

Our menu features traditional dishes and southern cuisine along with a few of our own creations and twists on the classics. If you're looking to experience authentic local food, served in a casual and friendly atmosphere, come visit our Food Truck today.

attending_trucks.name: Amkha Misky Peruvian Specialties
attending_trucks.about: We are a small family that love our culture and our cuisine. We love sharing our gastronomy with the beautiful state of Utah because we know how amazing it is. We hope you grow to love Peruvian food as much as we do and hope that it opens doors to exploring the beautiful culture that Peru holds.Come try our delicious empanadas which come in meat and vegetarian options or any of our other Peruvian specialties!

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

attending_trucks.name: Waffle Love
attending_trucks.about: A delicious gourmet waffle truck making liege waffles that have a caramelized & crispy exterior with a moist & dense interior, topped off with savory or sweet toppings that will make you want more!

attending_trucks.name: Freshies Lobster Co
attending_trucks.about: It started with two  New Englanders selling lobster rolls out of a 10x10 tent 10 years ago in Park City, they now have a restaurant and food truck in the Park City and Salt Lake area.  They are know for their very authentic and delicious Lobster Roll.  They do this by shipping in the lobster fresh from the shores of Maine and the bread is shipped from Maine as well.  Try our perfected, traditional, New England style fresh lobster roll (voted “World’s Best Lobster Roll” at the “Down East Lobster Roll Festival” competition in Portland, Maine!), lobster sliders, salads and more.

attending_trucks.name: Hungry Hawaiian
attending_trucks.about: The Hungry Hawaiian is a rebirth of my father's restaurant that was originally opened in 1978. We launched our restaurant in June 2017 and the food truck February 2018. Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

attending_trucks.name: Manouche
attending_trucks.about:
Manouche is a savory family-owned cuisine. Specializing in authentic, healthy meals prepared from the finest ingredients to create the perfect fusion of Greek, Mediterranean, and Middle- Eastern cuisine.
Our vision is to create a unique taste in which costumers will enjoy a one-of-a-kind experience.

Are you juggling between working from home and homeschooling housebound kids? You're plenty busy already! Don't worry about food, we have got your back. Whether you’re planning on having our kitchen over to cater for your event, having your scheduled weekly meals or you want to swing by.

We promise that our inventive healthy meals and attentive service will leave you truly satisfied. 
(Following the CDC guidelines).

attending_trucks.name: Bing's Korean Desserts
attending_trucks.about: Soon after returning home from a two year religious mission in South Korea, owners Trace Hicken and Chad Wallin came to find that one of their favorite desserts—bingsu was virtually impossible to find in Utah. Sitting around the dinner table of their rundown college dorm, they dreamed up the idea of bringing bingsu to Utah. With the help of fellow owners Tate Hicken and Marsha Wallin, In summer of 2020, Bing's Korean Desserts became a reality.

His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

Try our delicious kabobs or kalua pork; or our Filipino favorites like lumpia, pancit or pork adobo!

attending_trucks.name: Fatty Tuna Food
attending_trucks.about: Fatty Tuna food truck thrives on presenting our customers with tasteful authentic sushi and ramen through texture, spices, local produce and fresh fish. Come try our delicious ramen options of Tonkotsu Ramen, Shoyu Ramen, or Miso Ramen. Each have their own unique flavor for you to enjoy. We also serve the ever-popular sushi rolls such as the California roll, Vegas roll, and others!

attending_trucks.name: Porteña Gourmet Empanadas
attending_trucks.about: Flavors of home at your fingertips! Gourmet, fresh baked Argentinian empanadas.  We use a wide variety of flavors & textures, our empanadas are made with fresh seasonal ingredients that can satisfy your savory and sweet cravings.Porteña is proud to offer empanadas, a pastry pocket stuffed with a filling of your choice, that are meant to be shared around the table with your loved ones. We don't just feed people - we nourish them.

attending_trucks.name: Cluck Truck
attending_trucks.about: Do you love fried chicken? So do we! We serve fresh, delicious fried chicken wraps in a variety of tasty styles. Try the Original, a mango chipotle slaw with a honey chili drizzle or Greek, Hawaiian, Chinese or BBQ flavors!  Add a side of garlic parmesan fries for a real feast!All things Chicken! Delicious gourmet wraps with slaw. Chicken strips and fries (choice of regular potato fries with fry sauce or sweet potato fries with ranch.) For desserts there is a Brigadeiro (Brazillian cupcake) or 6” chocolate chip cookie or Bunuelos .

attending_trucks.name: Smoke a Billy BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Inspired by Rock a Billy and the best smoked and cooked meats around.  Our passion for authentic homestyle and original BBQ keeps us striving for the very best.  All of our entrees are made fresh to order - freshness & satisfaction guaranteed!

attending_trucks.name: Yoshi's Enso Grill
attending_trucks.about: Yoshi's Enso Grill is the food truck version of the popular Yoshi's Japanese Grill in Salt Lake City.  😀  We have sweet and spicy flavors in our rice bowls, sushi, egg rolls and more! We're sure we have something you will enjoy!

attending_trucks.name: Bruges
attending_trucks.about: Since 2004, Bruges shares the best loved foods from Belgium with Utah. Their food is not only fun, but it is authentic, artisan made with natural ingredients and prepared fresh for you. Try their unique sweet caramelized Liège waffle, award winning fries (frites) or famous Machine Gun Sandwich. Experience true Belgian indulgence without the jetlag.

attending_trucks.name: Comfort Bowl
attending_trucks.about: Just what it says . . . comfort food in a bowl! You’ll love their Japanese-style fried chicken and veggies covered with a sweet & spicy sauce. All of their bowls come included with lemongrass steamed rice and a Thai salad. Toss a few spring rolls on the side - you are sure to walk away pleased!Be sure to try their chicken katsu, which is their best seller. You won't be disappointed!

attending_trucks.name: Rickle's
attending_trucks.about: 6 different kinds of Phillys, plus pastas that are to die for. Then on top of that you add a meatball sub. All our recipes come from our very own kitchen, all the sauces and meat dishes are home made! Samich meals are all served along fries or home made potato chips with ranch seasoning. Our goal is to make your belly and wallet happy!

attending_trucks.name: Falafel Tree
attending_trucks.about: The Falafel Tree food truck delivers fresh and flavorful Mediterranean food, including fried falafel, Egyptian moussaka, homemade hummus, and fresh pita bread. Look for us at a nearby food truck rally or schedule us for your next event!Our specialty, falafel, is a deep-fried ball made from ground chickpeas with a combination of herbs and spices. None of the Falafel Tree menu contains any meat, dairy, or eggs (except upon request for catering events). Falafel Tree is run by native Egyptian, Chef Abby. His passion is to make people's tastebuds explode with amazing food and flavors. After opening our food truck in May 2017, we were nominated for the 10 Best Food Trucks in Utah.

attending_trucks.name: Curry Time
attending_trucks.about: We are an Indian food truck brought to you by India House restaurant located in Sandy, UT. We have been serving our delicious Indian cuisine to customers since 2001! Curry Time serves gourmet Indian cuisine -- curries, flat breads, and much more!  Our curries are made from the freshest ingredients, and our flatbreads are made in our imported Tandoor clay oven. Now we are bringing that mouth watering curry to the streets!

attending_trucks.name: District Thai Fusion
attending_trucks.about: "Thai so nice, you'll want to come back twice!" We serve up all the exotic flavors of authentic Thai food in traditional dishes to treat your tastebuds to a world of flavor. Start with an egg roll or a pork dumpling, then try one of our delectable curries or a pad thai entree! We have orange chicken and Teriyaki chicken, too!

attending_trucks.name: Smokin Star BBQ
attending_trucks.about: Welcome to the meat mecca of Smokin Star BBQ, which has perfected the art of slow cooked meats using the most flavorful, aromatic, perfectly seasoned cherry & pecan hardwood and self taught recipes. Our heaping platters or meat by the pound includes several daily meat choices as well as holiday specials. Our goal is to Serve bbq that gives one a foodgasmic experience!

attending_trucks.name: Fatty Tuna Food
attending_trucks.about: Fatty Tuna food truck thrives on presenting our customers with tasteful authentic sushi and ramen through texture, spices, local produce and fresh fish. Come try our delicious ramen options of Tonkotsu Ramen, Shoyu Ramen, or Miso Ramen. Each have their own unique flavor for you to enjoy. We also serve the ever-popular sushi rolls such as the California roll, Vegas roll, and others!

attending_trucks.name: Black’s Sliders
attending_trucks.about: Our food is hormone and antibiotic free and purchased from Wasatch meats , a local  vendor who holds the same vision of health through product excellence. We serve a variety of sliders and fries that everyone will love! Enjoy a choice of beef, chicken, pork or vegetarian sliders with toppings like cheddar cheese, caramelized onions & an array of fresh vegetables!  Don’t forget a side of our amazing, uniquely flavored fries!

attending_trucks.name: The Red Food Truck
attending_trucks.about: Delicious Peruvian-style sandwiches filled with savory meats & fresh veggies. Try our popular Lomo Saltado Sandwich. We start with a soft ciabatta roll loaded with grilled steak, peppers, onions and a special sauce that sets it apart from any sandwich you have ever had!

attending_trucks.name: Hungry Hawaiian
attending_trucks.about: The Hungry Hawaiian is a rebirth of my father's restaurant that was originally opened in 1978. We launched our restaurant in June 2017 and the food truck February 2018. Our mission is to serve quality Hawaiian flavors quickly and consistently. Everything we make, and serve is done with aloha. Enjoy "A taste of the islands with a touch of the Mainland."

attending_trucks.name: Yoshi's Enso Grill
attending_trucks.about: Yoshi's Enso Grill is the food truck version of the popular Yoshi's Japanese Grill in Salt Lake City.  😀  We have sweet and spicy flavors in our rice bowls, sushi, egg rolls and more! We're sure we have something you will enjoy!

attending_trucks.name: Papito Moes Puerto Rican Grub
attending_trucks.about: Papito Moe's is bringing Puerto Rican Flavor to Utah! We’ve come to Utah hungry to share traditional island favorites with you...Can you say Pernil, Mofongo, Tostones Empanadillas, and more?! Come Savor the Taste of the Island and put some WEPA in your step!

attending_trucks.name: Wings on Wheels
attending_trucks.about: A food truck/catering business with great customer service that is dedicated to serving fresh and delicious food. Our delicious wings are served with homemade sauces that will make your taste buds fall in love. Come and enjoy! We cater. Ask for the menu.

attending_trucks.name: Comfort Bowl
attending_trucks.about: Just what it says . . . comfort food in a bowl! You’ll love their Japanese-style fried chicken and veggies covered with a sweet & spicy sauce. All of their bowls come included with lemongrass steamed rice and a Thai salad. Toss a few spring rolls on the side - you are sure to walk away pleased!Be sure to try their chicken katsu, which is their best seller. You won't be disappointed!

attending_trucks.name: Traditions Mobile Cafe
attending_trucks.about: We aren't fast food, we're good food! We make gourmet sandwiches, burgers and hand cut fries. We source all our food locally and love bringing good food and happiness to everyone we serve!

attending_trucks.name: Balabe Senegalese Cuisine
attending_trucks.about: Beautiful Food Truck offering authentic Senegalese Cuisine at various events, festivals and office Lunches. Concession and Catering in Salt Lake Valley.  Started in 2018 with by a Senegalese Cuisine cook from New York City named Pape Sall.

attending_trucks.name: Papito Moes Puerto Rican Grub
attending_trucks.about: Papito Moe's is bringing Puerto Rican Flavor to Utah! We’ve come to Utah hungry to share traditional island favorites with you...Can you say Pernil, Mofongo, Tostones Empanadillas, and more?! Come Savor the Taste of the Island and put some WEPA in your step!

attending_trucks.name: El Sarten Italian Pasta
attending_trucks.about: We offer a variety of Italian Pasta, homemade sauces and many toppings. We specialize in combining your likes into your pasta. You choose your pasta, sauce, and toppings. Then our International chef will create an amazing combination just for you. Your perfect pasta!

attending_trucks.name: CupBop
attending_trucks.about: 'CUPBOP' is a new trend in Korean style take-out food. Korean BBQ in a cup! CupBop uses an amazing blend of spices & sauces to top your choice of rice, noodles, vegetables, pork, chicken or beef! Choose hot & spicy or sweet & tangy! Indulge in this Korean BBQ layered with pure goodness! Korean style veggie noodles with rice and a seasonal menu are also available.
